products_flowers.name: Biscotti Mintz
products_flowers.description:
Created for the real connoisseurs featuring two of the USA‚Äôs premium and most elusive strains. The lab crossed Biscotti; already a world beating 80% Indica dominant specimen with our exclusive and delicious Mintz Phenotype.

The results were stunning, the Cookies variant x OG Kush parentage provided the incredible potency and a flavour backbone, add the infusion of the creamy smooth Mintz genetics created this Mouth-watering new champion of a strain, a totally unique edition to our catalogue.

BISCOTTI MINTZ‚Ñ¢ is predominantly a deep purple plant with trichome production off the scale, during the final day‚Äôs leaves display a beautiful array of purples, oranges and greens wrapping the tightly formed bolder shaped dark green buds with bold purple highlights and long orange hairs.

You will be astounded by its tantalising, lingering tastes, and aromas, kushy flavours with hints of chocolate chip cookies with creamy mint and spice. Distinctive Limonene, Caryophyllene, Eucalyptol terpenes come together to produce exceptionally appetizing aroma.

With BISCOTTI MINTZ‚Ñ¢, discover a highly creative, focused, and relaxing effect with a noticeable and distinct creeping energizing body high.

products_flowers.name: Runtz of eden
products_flowers.description:
Runtz is an elite, sought-after strain that has been receiving a lot of well-deserved hype. The first time we grew it, the reason for all the hype was obvious. Runtz is absolutely covered in frost with some purple and violet hues mixed in. Runtz was created through a delicious cross of the infamous Zkittlez X Gelato strains. Runtz brings on a delicious fruity flavor with tropical citrus and sour berries with a spicy pineapple aftertaste. Runtz has been tested as high as 29% THC.

With Runtz of Eden, we were able to obtain the breeder‚Äôs cut of Forbidden Fruit that was the loudest purple strain we have ever encountered and crossed it with our prized Runtz cut. Runtz of Eden combines the LOUD sweet, rotten fruit terps with the exotic cookies and fruit and candy terpenes of Runtz. Phenos will produce varying amounts of purple colors.

products_flowers.name: Jokerz Candy
products_flowers.description:
Parents: Gummiez x Grape Gas
Aroma: Grape | Sweet
Flavour: Sweet and Sour | Diamond
In Melted Diamonds, Jokers Candy is an Indica dominant strain crossing Gummiez x Grape Gas! Giving off a slight grape gummy taste, it‚Äôs sweetness is not too overpowering with the balanced flavour of diamonds. Enjoy a sweet yet slightly sour strain that obtains the natural diamond aroma!

products_flowers.name: Slurricane
products_flowers.description:
Lineage	Do-Si-Dos x Purple Punch
Flavors	Sweet,Tropical, Earthy, Herbs, Berry
STRAIN INFORMATION
Slurricane Backstory

Slurricane is an indica dominant hybrid strain, created through a potent cross of the delicious Do-Si-Dos and the gorgeous Purple Punch strains. If you're an indica lover who appreciates a super flavorful smoke and a potent punch of effects, look no further. 

Slurricane will totally have you dazed with its delicious combination. This bud packs a super sweet fruity berry flavor accented by spicy tropical fruits and earth upon exhale. The aroma takes a pungent turn, with a spicy earthy overtone that's accented by herbs and berries. The Slurricane high settles in a few minutes after your first delicious exhale, creeping up on the back of your head with tingly effects before suddenly taking hold.

products_flowers.name: White Wedding
products_flowers.description:
Flavors Coffee, Creamy, Nutty, Sweet, Vanilla

White Wedding is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Wedding Cake and GSC. Bred by MSIKU, White Wedding is 25% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us White Wedding effects make them feel happy euphoric and talkative. Medical marijuana patients often choose White Wedding when dealing with symptoms associated with stress, anxiety, and depression. The dominant terpene of this cannabis strain is pinene. White Wedding features an aroma and flavor profile of vanilla, apple, and ammonia. If you‚Äôve smoked, dabbed, or consumed White Wedding, tell us about your experience by leaving a strain review.

products_flowers.name: Platinum Kush
products_flowers.description:
Platinum Kush, also known as Platinum OG, is a West Coast staple that first emerged in the early 1990s as a hybrid of Master Kush with the landrace Afghani. Sources speculate that the strain is instead a cross of OG Kush and Afghani, and different varieties with the same name may exist on the market.

At full maturity, Platinum Kush is a squat, bushy plant with wide, dark leaves and medium-sized buds. Its flower tends to be densely packed, colored with orange hairs and resinous trichomes. Platinum Kush is known for its hardiness, making a suitable crop for either indoor or outdoor growing, even in colder climates. The strain flowers in 8-9 weeks indoors and late September outdoors in the Northern Hemisphere, March in the Southern Hemisphere.

products_flowers.name: Platinum Scout V2
products_flowers.description:
An Indica-dominant hybrid cross of Durban Poison x OG Kush, our unique pheno of Platinum Scout was popped from seeds from Pacific Seed Bank. With dense, bright green buds and robust trichome production, the Platinum Scout strain is a potent cultivar for sufferers of pain and inflammation.
PHYSICAL EFFECTS

Relaxing, Anti-Inflammatory, Hazy
FLAVOR

Dank, Creamy, Cookies

products_flowers.name: Kush x Mintz
products_flowers.description: Kush Mints, also known as "Kush Mintz," is a hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing Animal Mints with Bubba Kush. The result is a high THC strain with a unique minty taste. Kush Mints provides effects that are uplifting and happy. This strain has a complex flavor profile that tastes like mint and cookies. Growers say Kush Mints grows best when indoors and done hydroponically. Medical marijuana patients choose this strain to help stimulate appetite.

products_flowers.name: 91 Octane
products_flowers.description:
91 Octane Exotic Genetix cannabis seeds is a hybrid birthed from a cross of Biscotti x Scotty 2 Hotty.

Biscotti flowers into small, dense buds marked by dark green and purple foliage with bright orange pistils.

The striking trichome coverage of this strain gives it top shelf appeal.

While you may dismiss its tiny popcorn buds at first glance, these nugs are sticky to the touch.

This strain tastes like sweet cookies with undertones of diesel, giving you an enjoyable experience that‚Äôs great for both mind and body.

The aroma is earthy and herbal, mixed with fruits, while the taste has hints of sweetness from start to finish.

Scotty 2 Hotty  is a hybrid birthed from a cross of Biscotti x Rainbow Chip.

Thanks to the Scotty she‚Äôs got that weight and density.

This girl hits that biscotti HARD. Cookie nose, dripping in resin. Flecks of purple starting to come out.

This strain give heavy gassy luxuriotti vibes as you would expect from another biscotti strain!

Sticky triched out buds with beautiful greens purples and oranges throughout the bud.

The smoke has a smoothness of a Gary Payton with that biscotti funk lightened up by that rainbow chip.

products_flowers.name: Compound Z
products_flowers.description: Compound Z is an indica dominant strain with a lineage of Apples & Bananas crossed with White Runtz. You get a gassy, fruity aroma along with a sweet and spicy flavor profile from this delectable strain. Compound Z has a happy, relaxing high that sets into your body, helping to combat chronic pain, stress and anxiety. The perfect strain for consumers who want to take the edge off after a stressful day.

products_flowers.name: Tarts
products_flowers.description:
Exotic Genetix Tarts
Tarts is a mostly indica variety from Exotic Genetix and can be cultivated indoors (where the plants will need a flowering time of ¬±60 days) and outdoors. Exotic Genetix' Tarts is a THC dominant variety

products_flowers.name: Truffle Cake
products_flowers.description: Believed to be a strain born in California Truffle Cake is a slightly Sativa-dominant (60% Sativa/ 40% Indica) hybrid with an appearance much like an OG, and a potency associated with the best OG Kush cuts. However, the strain has an unusual terpene profile as it is almost completely lack odor. The buds of Truffle Cake are pretty dense, large-sized, and feature an enormous coating of crystal trichomes that film the leaves with a silvery-black effect. When cured and burned, this flower gives off a faint hint dank pine. Truffle Cake Cannabis strain is a trufflez group sativa ‚Äì a daytime strain and a top choice for creative people. Its effects start with a cerebral rush that is felt almost immediately. The strain has a capacity for intense focus and energy. Although Truffle Cake strain is an introspective strain that is useful for brainstorming and problem-solving, it has a high that can be essentially described as perfectly balanced, given its equal head and body effect. Beginners are advised to use in small doses, as the high could be overwhelming, leading to paranoia or increased levels of anxiety. 31% THC
